'''抽动障碍'''（英文：'''Tics'''、'''Tic Disorder'''），为一种發病於兒童時期的[[精神疾病|精神疾病]]，發病時會出現抽動行為，例如肌肉會不自主、无目的、快速的收缩。此類疾病男患者多于女患者<ref>{{cite news |title=儿童抽动障碍诊断与治疗专家共识(2017实用版) |url=http://rs.yiigle.com/m/CN101070201715/1004566.htm |publisher=中華實用兒科臨床雜誌}}</ref><ref name=BehaveNet> [[American_Psychiatric_Association|American Psychiatric Association]] (2000). [http://behavenet.com/capsules/disorders/touretteTR.htm DSM-IV-TR: Tourette's Disorder.] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090413173204/http://behavenet.com/capsules/disorders/touretteTR.htm |date=2009-04-13 }} ''Diagnostic and Statistical Manual of Mental Disorders''， 4th ed., text revision ([[DSM-IV-TR|DSM-IV-TR]]), ISBN 0890420254. Available at BehaveNet.com Retrieved on August 10, 2009.</ref><ref name=Swain>Swain JE, Scahill L, Lombroso PJ, King RA, Leckman JF. "Tourette syndrome and tic disorders: a decade of progress".  ''J Am Acad Child Adolesc Psychiatry''. 2007 Aug;46（8）:947–68 PMID 17667475 </ref>。

